OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FFootage released on Sunday suggested
OL,10,Fthat the United States may have been
OL,11,Fresponsible for a deadly attack on a
OL,12,Fschool in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
