PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump had previously
OL,7,Fsaid Iran was responsible for the
OL,8,Fattack, but when the weapon was
OL,9,Fidentified as a Tomahawk missile, the
OL,10,Fevidence seemed to contradict that
OL,11,Fstatement, because the US is the only
OL,12,Fcountry participating in the Iran
OL,13,Fconflict which is known to have that
OL,14,Fparticular type of missile.
OL,16,FThe US president has made several bold
OL,17,Fstatements about his country's weapon
OL,18,Fcapabilities since February 28, when
OL,19,FIsrael and the US launched joint
OL,20,Fairstrikes on Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
