OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FTrump has said the US has the ability
OL,7,Fto hit Iran "20 times harder than they
OL,8,Fhave been hit thus far" and claimed
OL,9,Fthe country has "a virtually unlimited
OL,10,Fsupply of medium and upper medium
OL,11,Fgrade munitions".
OL,13,FITV News explains what the US has in
OL,14,Fits arsenal.
OL,16,FHow much does the US spend on weapons?
OL,18,FThe United States has the most
OL,19,Fpowerful and best-funded military in
OL,20,Fthe world, and spends $997 billion
OL,21,F(#741bn) every year on defence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
