OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FThis is a list of some of the weapons
OL,7,Fdeployed by the US so far in what the
OL,8,FPentagon has called "Operation Epic
OL,9,FFury", along with their estimated cost
OL,10,Fif publicly available, as reported by
OL,11,FITV News' US partner CNN.
OL,13,FCould the US run out of weapons?
OL,15,FAs the war between the US, Israel and
OL,16,FIran continues, there are questions
OL,17,Fover how many weapons the US can
OL,18,Fafford to use in this conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
