OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump has suggested
OL,7,Fthat the country has an endless supply
OL,8,Fof certain types of weapons.
OL,10,F"We have a virtually unlimited supply
OL,11,Fof Medium and Upper Medium Grade
OL,12,FMunitions, which we are using, as an
OL,13,Fexample, in Iran, and recently used in
OL,14,FVenezuela," Trump wrote on Truth
OL,15,FSocial on March 6.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
