OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FHe had written on February 27 that
OL,7,Fseveral defence contractors had agreed
OL,8,Fto quadruple production of weapons "as
OL,9,Frapidly as possible," but he did not
OL,10,Fspecify what exactly was being
OL,11,Fmanufactured.
OL,13,FSean Parnell, the Pentagon's chief
OL,14,Fspokesman, similarly said in a
OL,15,Fstatement last week that the US
OL,16,Fmilitary "has everything it needs to
OL,17,Fexecute any mission at the time and
OL,18,Fplace of the president's choosing and
OL,19,Fon any timeline".
