OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,F"I'm not particularly worried about us
OL,7,Factually running out during this
OL,8,Fconflict," Ryan Brobst, a scholar
OL,9,Ffocused on US defence strategy at the
OL,10,FFoundation for Defense of Democracies,
OL,11,Ftold Associated Press. "It's about
OL,12,Fdeterring China and Russia the day
OL,13,Fafter this conflict is over."
OL,15,FMissile defence systems are believed
OL,16,Fto be under the most strain, Mr Brobst
OL,17,Fsaid, with Patriot and Terminal High
OL,18,FAltitude Area Defense (THAAD)
OL,19,Finterceptors in high demand in Ukraine
OL,20,Fand Israel, respectively.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]sD@XOUuD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
