OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FAnd some Democratic lawmakers have
OL,7,Fquestioned the long-term impact on the
OL,8,FUS and its allies.
OL,10,F"We've been told again and again and
OL,11,Fagain one reason that we can't provide
OL,12,Finterceptors for the Patriot system or
OL,13,Fother munitions for Ukraine is that
OL,14,Fthey're in short supply," Senator
OL,15,FRichard Blumenthal told CNN on
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,18,FWhat about the people power?
OL,20,FThere are 1.3 million active service
OL,21,Fpersonnel in the US.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
