OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FThere is no definitive number of how
OL,7,Fmany Americans are involved in the
OL,8,Fconflict in Iran, but the US military
OL,9,Fconfirmed on Monday that a seventh US
OL,10,Fservice member was killed during the
OL,11,Foperations.
OL,13,FTrump warned of possible casualties in
OL,14,Fa video on March 1 after the first
OL,15,Fthree deaths were confirmed.
OL,17,F"Sadly, there will likely be more
OL,18,F(deaths) before it ends," Trump said,
OL,19,Fbefore adding: "That's the way it is.
OL,20,FLikely be more."
OL,26,@zD@ApmzD@HpnzD@YO]{D@POU|D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
