OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,F"But we'll do everything possible
OL,7,Fwhere that won't be the case."
OL,9,FSome Democrats were critical of the
OL,10,Fresponse at the time and suggested
OL,11,FTrump's remarks were more businesslike
OL,12,Fthan was sensitive to the families of
OL,13,Fthose who had died.
OL,15,FWhere does the US have bases?
OL,17,FThe US has about 750`800 military
OL,18,Fsites in more than 70 countries,
OL,19,Fthrough its army, air force and navy,
OL,20,Fall across the world, including in:
