OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FHow does the US stack up against Iran?
OL,8,FTrump said on Truth Social the US
OL,9,Fcould hit Iran "20 times harder" than
OL,10,Fthe current activity on the ground, in
OL,11,Fthe air and at sea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
