OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773220132
OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,F"If Iran does anything that stops the
OL,7,Fflow of Oil within the Strait of
OL,8,FHormuz, they will be hit by the United
OL,9,FStates of America TWENTY TIMES HARDER
OL,10,Fthan they have been hit thus far.
OL,11,FAdditionally, we will take out easily
OL,12,Fdestroyable targets that will make it
OL,13,Fvirtually impossible for Iran to ever
OL,14,Fbe built back, as a Nation, again `
OL,15,FDeath, Fire, and Fury will reign upon
OL,16,Fthem," he wrote on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
