OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FWhile it is impossible to say exactly
OL,7,Fwhat that means in terms of weapons,
OL,8,Fit is true that Iran is much smaller
OL,9,Fand less equipped than the US in terms
OL,10,Fof its military.
OL,12,FIts active military is around half the
OL,13,Fsize in terms of personnel - around
OL,14,F610,000 in total - but Iran has one of
OL,15,Fthe largest and most diverse missile
OL,16,Farsenals in the Middle East, according
OL,17,Fto defence analysts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
