OL,3,CWhat weapons are the US using in Iran
OL,4,Cand how powerful are they?
OL,6,FThat includes mortars, rockets, drones
OL,7,Fand cruise missiles, which are
OL,8,Fdesigned to fly at low altitudes and
OL,9,Fstrike targets on the ground, and the
OL,10,Fexact number of Iran's missiles is
OL,11,Funclear.
